			</p>
		</li>
		<li>
				<title>Span of a set of Vectors</title>
			<p>
				The <em>span of a set of vectors</em><idx><h>vector</h><h>span</h></idx> <m>\left\{\vec{v}_1,\, \vec{v}_2,\, \ldots\, \vec{v}_n\right\}</m> over a field <m>\mathbb{F}</m> is the set of all linear combinations of the form
				<me>a_1\vec{v}_1+a_2\vec{v}_2+a_3\vec{v}_3+\cdots+a_n\vec{v}_n</me>
				where <m>a_i\in\mathbb{F}</m> for all <m>i</m>.
